- Ronnie, là em đây.

542
00:26:42,084 --> 00:26:43,284


543
00:26:43,286 --> 00:26:45,957


544
00:26:45,959 --> 00:26:47,693
Caitlin.

545
00:26:47,695 --> 00:26:50,429


546
00:26:50,431 --> 00:26:51,897
Cisco có ở đó không?

